WEBVTT

01:40.610 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.259 --> 01:48.800
[Episode 9]

01:49.729 --> 01:50.420
No.

01:50.860 --> 01:52.660
After all, he's still my father.

01:52.780 --> 01:54.340
-Can't you just...
-Apple.

01:55.539 --> 01:57.000
I don't like mealy apples.

02:20.490 --> 02:21.450
I have to go.

02:21.980 --> 02:24.040
Call me when you've made up your mind.

02:44.170 --> 02:45.829
You're quite confident, huh?

02:46.590 --> 02:47.780
What makes you think

02:47.800 --> 02:49.400
I'd eat anything you feed me?

02:51.770 --> 02:53.829
Do you want her to keep bothering you?

02:56.700 --> 02:57.960
I'm not afraid of that.

02:59.140 --> 02:59.940
Really?

03:00.450 --> 03:02.780
Not even afraid of a woman
clinging to you?

03:05.220 --> 03:06.820
What's there to be afraid of?

03:07.900 --> 03:10.500
It depends on
which woman we're talking about.

03:12.980 --> 03:13.940
Wan Qing?

03:15.760 --> 03:17.420
She's nothing to be afraid of.

03:18.610 --> 03:19.940
What about other women?

03:23.329 --> 03:24.010
Who?

03:24.860 --> 03:26.060
Who are you afraid of?

03:41.420 --> 03:42.420
In my entire life,

03:42.780 --> 03:44.640
I've never been afraid of anyone.

03:54.170 --> 03:55.300
You sure about that?

03:55.820 --> 03:57.420
Maybe one day you'll meet a woman

03:57.420 --> 03:59.280
you're really, really afraid of.

04:12.940 --> 04:13.980
If that day comes,

04:14.110 --> 04:15.240
I'll accept my fate.

04:20.810 --> 04:21.579
I specially found you

04:21.579 --> 04:23.050
a coach who speaks Chinese.

04:23.050 --> 04:23.580
This one.

04:23.860 --> 04:24.610
Coach Hua.

04:24.900 --> 04:25.700
Hello, Coach.

04:25.930 --> 04:27.860
I've been a top coach for ten years.

04:28.020 --> 04:29.540
You can trust me.

05:03.980 --> 05:05.220
Congratulations, my lucky star,

05:05.220 --> 05:06.950
for passing your driving test!

05:07.020 --> 05:08.290
It's all thanks to you.

05:08.690 --> 05:10.890
It's because you're naturally gifted.

05:12.690 --> 05:14.460
Actually, I don't even know why,

05:14.460 --> 05:16.120
but the moment I first saw you,

05:16.370 --> 05:17.860
I just wanted to be close to you.

05:17.860 --> 05:19.050
That's no mystery.

05:19.220 --> 05:21.480
It's because you're beautiful and kind.

05:21.690 --> 05:23.550
Stop teasing. I'm being serious.

05:23.930 --> 05:26.340
It might be a connection
from our past lives.

05:26.340 --> 05:27.020
That's it.

05:27.220 --> 05:28.080
It's called...

05:28.420 --> 05:29.540
"instant..."

05:29.930 --> 05:31.260
"Instant connection!"

05:32.230 --> 05:33.659
Your Chinese is really good.

05:33.659 --> 05:34.860
You even know idioms.

05:49.460 --> 05:50.490
Xin,

05:52.020 --> 05:54.130
why did your grades drop so fast?

05:55.290 --> 05:56.980
Did you not understand the lessons?

05:56.980 --> 05:57.730
Xin,

05:57.980 --> 05:59.110
you must study hard.

05:59.490 --> 06:01.610
If I had studied hard back then,

06:01.780 --> 06:03.310
I wouldn't be a hoodlum now.

06:03.460 --> 06:04.630
Are you cut out for studying?

06:04.630 --> 06:05.610
Back then, a C was already

06:05.610 --> 06:08.210
-way beyond your usual performance.
-Go away.

06:08.250 --> 06:09.510
I've gotten a C before.

06:13.550 --> 06:14.660
You must

06:15.050 --> 06:16.310
take my words to heart.

06:16.660 --> 06:18.340
Okay, okay. I got it.

06:19.730 --> 06:20.860
You really did?

06:21.690 --> 06:23.750
Then I'll sign this for you this time.

06:34.610 --> 06:35.490
Wait, Xin.

06:36.020 --> 06:38.340
Do you understand
all the questions you got wrong now?

06:38.340 --> 06:39.460
Let me tell you,

06:39.610 --> 06:41.220
making mistakes isn't scary.

06:41.220 --> 06:41.860
What's scary is...

06:41.860 --> 06:43.260
I think you're the scary.

06:43.610 --> 06:45.580
Are you signing it or not? If not, I will.

06:45.580 --> 06:46.780
Why so many words?

06:49.810 --> 06:50.490
Xin,

06:50.730 --> 06:52.290
how do you write Jin in Jin Zhao?

06:52.290 --> 06:53.810
-Give me a break.
-With your education level...

06:53.810 --> 06:55.050
Give it to me. I'll sign it.

06:55.050 --> 06:56.710
I just can't recall right now.

06:56.980 --> 06:57.710
Let me think.

06:57.780 --> 06:58.810
So rusty. Give it to me.

06:58.810 --> 07:00.050
Do you even know how to sign it?
Give it to me.

07:00.050 --> 07:01.220
-Who's going to sign it?
-Me.

07:01.220 --> 07:01.980
I will. Give it to me.

07:01.980 --> 07:03.490
-Let me.
-You know how to write it?

07:03.490 --> 07:04.580
You don't know how to write it.
How can you sign it?

07:04.580 --> 07:06.150
I'll sign it now. I remember it now.

07:06.150 --> 07:07.750
-Give it to me.
-I'll sign it.

07:08.930 --> 07:09.660
Brandy.

07:11.680 --> 07:12.330
Well...

07:12.460 --> 07:13.860
Brandy, don't get angry.

07:13.900 --> 07:16.090
One test doesn't mean anything.

07:16.570 --> 07:18.900
Right. Xin's actually been working hard.

07:20.970 --> 07:22.490
Yes, she got an A before.

07:22.610 --> 07:23.860
She even got an A+ once. I signed those.

07:23.860 --> 07:24.930
You... shut up!

07:39.020 --> 07:41.150
These last two questions aren't hard.

07:41.490 --> 07:43.090
Why did you leave them blank?

07:43.130 --> 07:44.190
I did it on purpose.

07:45.370 --> 07:46.050
Why?

07:46.370 --> 07:47.290
The teacher said the first-place student

07:47.290 --> 07:49.460
needs to give a speech
as the student representative.

07:49.460 --> 07:50.460
I don't want to go.

07:52.220 --> 07:54.580
You're getting more and more
strong-willed as you grow up.

07:54.580 --> 07:57.100
Not bad.
I've only ever written reflections,

07:57.100 --> 07:58.460
never given a speech.

07:59.610 --> 08:01.020
I was afraid my mom would nag.

08:01.020 --> 08:03.220
I didn't expect you guys to be even worse.

08:03.220 --> 08:04.620
She's talking about you.

08:06.100 --> 08:07.170
I'll sign it for you this time.

08:07.170 --> 08:08.460
Next time,

08:08.640 --> 08:09.370
just talk to your teacher.

08:09.370 --> 08:10.810
Don't pull these little tricks.

08:10.810 --> 08:11.610
I see.

08:11.930 --> 08:13.060
Yang, take her home.

08:13.290 --> 08:14.130
Yes, Master.

08:18.460 --> 08:19.750
Go now.

08:23.770 --> 08:25.030
Be careful on your way.

08:27.050 --> 08:29.050
Aren't you a bit too strict with Xin?

08:29.200 --> 08:31.000
Too harsh. She's just a kid.

08:31.020 --> 08:31.890
Indeed.

08:35.580 --> 08:37.780
You two have pretended to be her parents

08:37.980 --> 08:40.440
signing her papers many times,
haven't you?

08:44.300 --> 08:45.580
I'm... I'm thirsty?

08:46.030 --> 08:47.180
You want to buy a dog?

08:47.860 --> 08:48.860
I sell cats too.

08:49.000 --> 08:50.450
-I'm right next to the shop.
-The connection is bad.

08:49.330 --> 08:51.410
[Speeding Auto House]

08:50.860 --> 08:52.130
I'll move somewhere else to talk.

08:52.130 --> 08:52.610
Alright, alright.

08:52.610 --> 08:53.460
-I'll go somewhere else.
-Okay, okay.

08:53.460 --> 08:54.260
Just a moment.

09:02.460 --> 09:03.100
I...

09:03.830 --> 09:04.790
I'm thirsty.

09:34.180 --> 09:36.370
Hello, one milk tea please.

09:37.700 --> 09:39.730
Here's your milk tea. Welcome back.

09:39.860 --> 09:40.860
Thank you.

09:48.980 --> 09:49.980
This looks cool.

09:51.480 --> 09:53.100
The skills
are a bit rough compared to mine.

09:53.100 --> 09:54.300
You're bragging.

09:57.940 --> 09:59.610
Has the locking collar been adjusted?

09:59.610 --> 10:00.470
How do you know?

10:01.220 --> 10:02.130
Is it that obvious?

10:02.130 --> 10:04.370
There was a noise when you drove in.

10:04.770 --> 10:05.580
It's loose.

10:05.840 --> 10:06.860
I just modified this car.

10:06.860 --> 10:08.460
Can you check it again for me?

10:09.130 --> 10:09.820
See that?

10:10.200 --> 10:11.370
Indeed.

10:11.830 --> 10:13.030
Right? And look here.

10:13.860 --> 10:15.820
This engine doesn't suit this car.

10:17.100 --> 10:17.890
And look,

10:18.700 --> 10:20.060
the right locking collar is also broken.

10:20.060 --> 10:21.460
It needs to be fixed too, okay?

10:21.460 --> 10:22.340
Okay.

10:22.820 --> 10:23.700
Lin Sui?

10:24.610 --> 10:25.700
Why is he here?

10:28.060 --> 10:33.360
[locking collar]

10:34.730 --> 10:35.820
Why are you here?

10:38.940 --> 10:40.650
I'm meeting a friend here.

10:44.500 --> 10:46.430
You picked the worst-tasting one.

10:47.770 --> 10:48.580
This one?

10:51.180 --> 10:52.800
Which flavor tastes better then?

10:52.800 --> 10:53.560
Come with me.

11:16.940 --> 11:18.200
I don't drink alcohol.

11:19.040 --> 11:20.130
Don't accuse me wrongly.

11:20.130 --> 11:21.860
This doesn't have any alcohol.

11:26.300 --> 11:27.060
Don't worry.

11:27.410 --> 11:28.410
No peach either.

11:31.340 --> 11:32.100
Thanks.

11:37.180 --> 11:38.580
It's strawberry flavor?

11:39.590 --> 11:40.720
Welcome to my world.

11:43.770 --> 11:44.500
Hey, Lin Sui.

11:45.060 --> 11:45.990
We should go now.

11:49.300 --> 11:50.940
Going up the mountain?
I can give you a ride.

11:50.940 --> 11:51.600
No, thanks.

11:51.840 --> 11:54.370
I arranged to meet Sanlai
at the service area.

11:54.410 --> 11:55.250
Sanlai?

11:56.730 --> 11:57.990
He's the one I invited.

11:58.010 --> 12:00.010
You could wait for him up the mountain.

12:00.010 --> 12:02.210
You invited him? So you know each other?

12:03.250 --> 12:04.650
Not really.

12:05.340 --> 12:06.300
Just curious.

12:07.340 --> 12:08.410
Curious?

12:09.250 --> 12:10.450
Are you coming or not?

12:15.220 --> 12:17.300
I'm lost. Wait for me on the mountain.

12:18.980 --> 12:19.820
Which car?

12:20.610 --> 12:21.370
That one.

12:21.980 --> 12:22.540
Let's go.

12:49.010 --> 12:50.140
What does this mean?

12:50.700 --> 12:52.940
It's an understanding between drivers,

12:52.940 --> 12:54.100
like a secret code.

12:55.840 --> 12:58.100
Aren't you going to note it in your phone?

12:58.940 --> 13:00.070
It's not necessary.

13:04.290 --> 13:05.170
Hold on tight.

13:13.810 --> 13:14.870
Don't touch it yet.

13:15.220 --> 13:17.150
The engine's really hot right now.

13:19.460 --> 13:20.720
Why hasn't he come yet?

13:40.820 --> 13:41.820
Lin Sui, look.

13:42.220 --> 13:45.080
That cute little pickup
is heading up the mountain.

13:50.010 --> 13:51.610
Do you think that guy is faking it?

13:51.610 --> 13:52.490
If not,

13:52.650 --> 13:53.860
it's even funnier.

13:56.730 --> 13:58.890
Why did you call Sanlai here?

14:00.820 --> 14:01.820
That's something

14:02.060 --> 14:03.120
I'm wondering too.

14:13.960 --> 14:15.340
Sanlai, what took you so long?

14:15.340 --> 14:17.010
I've been waiting for you for an hour.

14:17.010 --> 14:18.010
What's the rush?

14:18.180 --> 14:19.250
It's such a big event.

14:19.250 --> 14:21.450
I had to get myself properly dressed up.

14:22.770 --> 14:24.130
The outfit looks good.

14:24.340 --> 14:26.340
But that red scarf...

14:27.250 --> 14:28.450
You have great taste.

14:28.890 --> 14:30.020
This is for good luck—

14:30.020 --> 14:32.050
it means a victorious start.

14:34.180 --> 14:34.890
Do you know

14:35.130 --> 14:36.490
when you were driving earlier,

14:36.490 --> 14:37.350
that camera...

14:37.350 --> 14:38.160
Well...

14:40.860 --> 14:42.030
Let's get started.

14:45.460 --> 14:46.250
Let's go.

14:49.040 --> 14:49.730
Good luck.

15:09.810 --> 15:10.690
Brandy said

15:10.770 --> 15:12.130
this car is modified.

15:12.460 --> 15:14.460
1000 HP, 2000 torque,

15:14.490 --> 15:17.550
Wankel engine.
It's faster than race cars on the track.

15:22.530 --> 15:23.460
Sorry.

15:23.860 --> 15:25.110
I didn't mean to take advantage of you.

15:25.110 --> 15:26.960
I should be a good host.

15:27.860 --> 15:29.460
I'll give you a 5-second head start.

15:29.460 --> 15:30.180
How's that?

15:30.940 --> 15:33.300
Then I'll respectfully accept your offer.

15:33.300 --> 15:34.830
The guest follows the host.

15:42.060 --> 15:42.650
Sanlai,

15:42.680 --> 15:44.080
are you okay? Be careful.

15:45.340 --> 15:46.100
I'm fine.

15:46.250 --> 15:47.300
I just used a little trick

15:47.300 --> 15:48.760
and gained the upper hand.

15:48.770 --> 15:49.340
Go back.

16:04.610 --> 16:06.060
Let's go!

16:06.180 --> 16:07.130
Let's move!

16:32.820 --> 16:33.940
Looks like...

16:34.980 --> 16:36.310
it won't take 5 seconds.

16:38.060 --> 16:38.730
I realized

16:38.860 --> 16:40.890
we need to follow the rules in games.

16:41.250 --> 16:42.530
You don't need
to let me go first this time.

16:42.530 --> 16:43.590
Let's go together.

16:44.100 --> 16:45.180
Give me the hat.

16:47.850 --> 16:48.900
Give it to me.

16:51.880 --> 16:52.980
This hat isn't mine.

16:52.980 --> 16:54.710
I need to return it to its owner.

16:54.770 --> 16:56.030
I'll return it for you.

17:01.970 --> 17:03.060
There's a good cupcake shop

17:03.060 --> 17:05.190
at the service area down the mountain.

17:05.970 --> 17:06.819
See you there.

17:08.440 --> 17:11.040
If you get there within half an hour,
it's on me.

17:14.740 --> 17:16.670
Today really got off to a bad start.

17:16.930 --> 17:18.500
All this dressing up was for nothing.

17:18.500 --> 17:21.700
You're a typical underachiever
with lots of stationery.

17:22.819 --> 17:24.260
Alright, let's head back.

17:24.260 --> 17:25.540
Going up the mountain was so difficult.

17:25.540 --> 17:26.890
Going down must be much easier.

17:26.890 --> 17:27.740
You're wrong.

17:28.030 --> 17:30.360
The downhill road is the hardest to drive.

17:32.500 --> 17:34.030
Why do I feel a little dizzy?

17:36.170 --> 17:37.020
I'll drive.

17:47.340 --> 17:48.300
Jiang Mu,

17:48.820 --> 17:49.650
are you sure?

17:49.650 --> 17:51.510
It took me over an hour to drive up.

17:51.650 --> 17:52.450
Don't worry.

17:52.570 --> 17:55.230
We'll definitely get there
within half an hour.

18:11.800 --> 18:13.520
She only took 23 minutes.

18:15.890 --> 18:16.500
Hello.

18:16.690 --> 18:17.820
Hello, sir.

18:19.130 --> 18:21.410
Two of each: black tea, green tea,

18:21.410 --> 18:22.130
and lemon flavors.

18:22.130 --> 18:24.930
And two without cream.

18:25.120 --> 18:27.500
Sanlai,
why are you only buying the cake bases?

18:27.500 --> 18:28.630
They're for Brandy.

18:29.080 --> 18:30.270
Brandy never eats

18:30.300 --> 18:31.340
the cream on cake.

18:31.610 --> 18:32.890
I don't even know

18:32.890 --> 18:35.090
what's left of a cupcake without cream.

18:35.370 --> 18:36.970
He's not really into sweets.

18:37.370 --> 18:39.170
You know he doesn't like sweets?

18:39.240 --> 18:40.330
That habit of his

18:40.450 --> 18:41.980
is a bit annoying, isn't it?

18:45.380 --> 18:45.980
By the way,

18:46.130 --> 18:48.190
why did Lin Sui take your hat earlier?

18:48.860 --> 18:49.740
I have no idea.

18:49.890 --> 18:51.290
That guy is pretty weird.

18:51.540 --> 18:52.170
I already told him

18:52.170 --> 18:53.210
that the hat wasn't mine

18:53.210 --> 18:54.610
and that I needed to return it
to its owner.

18:54.610 --> 18:56.130
But Lin said,

18:56.580 --> 18:58.540
"I'll return it to him for you."

18:59.000 --> 19:00.040
Ridiculous.

19:00.060 --> 19:01.410
Does he even know whose hat it is?

19:01.410 --> 19:02.170
Whose is it?

19:03.060 --> 19:03.930
It's Brandy's.

19:05.860 --> 19:07.710
Sir, your cakes are ready.

19:08.820 --> 19:10.550
Thanks. How much is it in total?

19:10.820 --> 19:12.480
Someone already paid for you.

19:13.040 --> 19:13.740
Already paid?

19:13.740 --> 19:14.370
Yes.

19:23.090 --> 19:24.130
Who was it?

19:25.210 --> 19:26.060
Sanlai,

19:26.430 --> 19:28.110
do you know how long it took us

19:28.130 --> 19:29.990
to get down the mountain just now?

19:30.100 --> 19:30.970
Not sure.

19:32.570 --> 19:33.500
40 or 50 minutes?

19:34.860 --> 19:36.780
23 minutes.

19:37.020 --> 19:38.420
23 minutes?

19:47.060 --> 19:48.580
Turn on the lights
if you want to take photos with the car.

19:48.580 --> 19:50.020
Hey handsome, you're cute!

19:50.020 --> 19:51.170
Can we take a photo with you?

19:51.170 --> 19:53.540
Come on, come on, together.

19:54.540 --> 19:55.130
Make me look cool.

19:55.130 --> 19:57.500
Three, two, one.

19:57.970 --> 19:59.210
One more, one more!

19:59.210 --> 20:00.290
Come on.

20:01.260 --> 20:02.460
Thank you, handsome.

20:03.020 --> 20:03.650
Thanks!

20:03.650 --> 20:05.080
You're welcome.

20:05.100 --> 20:05.860
Your car looks great too.

20:05.860 --> 20:07.260
-Thank you. You have good taste!
-Bye-bye.

20:07.260 --> 20:08.600
Don't forget me
next time you want to take a photo.

20:08.600 --> 20:09.080
Sure.

20:09.100 --> 20:09.820
Bye-bye!

20:10.210 --> 20:10.930
Sanlai,

20:11.100 --> 20:12.860
looks like you're quite popular.

20:12.860 --> 20:13.970
So why do you make yourself

20:13.970 --> 20:14.750
look like this?

20:14.750 --> 20:16.540
Why don't you spruce yourself up a bit?

20:16.540 --> 20:17.610
Look like what?

20:17.810 --> 20:19.740
I put a lot of effort into this look.

20:19.820 --> 20:20.970
Yes, I can see that.

20:21.260 --> 20:23.450
It's just that your hair

20:23.660 --> 20:25.320
is kind of covering your eyes.

20:32.260 --> 20:33.060
Well,

20:33.430 --> 20:36.040
it's mainly because I'm just too charming.

20:36.560 --> 20:37.860
I'm afraid the girls
will be so distracted when they see me

20:37.860 --> 20:38.340
that they won't be able to move,

20:38.340 --> 20:40.060
and it'll affect my pet shop business.

20:40.060 --> 20:40.740
That's why

20:41.370 --> 20:43.060
I make my handsomeness

20:43.170 --> 20:44.780
look a bit mysterious.

20:45.740 --> 20:48.000
You really put a lot of thought into that.

20:48.050 --> 20:48.730
Of course.

20:49.970 --> 20:51.410
I mean it.

20:51.540 --> 20:53.110
If you trim your beard

20:53.130 --> 20:54.820
and cut your hair a bit shorter,

20:54.820 --> 20:56.860
you may look much fresher.

20:59.060 --> 20:59.990
Are you serious?

21:00.340 --> 21:01.060
Yes.

21:02.320 --> 21:04.110
I think maybe you'll even become

21:04.110 --> 21:05.680
more popular than Brandy.

21:07.600 --> 21:08.250
Girl,

21:08.820 --> 21:10.210
since you said that,

21:10.500 --> 21:11.480
I'll have to

21:11.500 --> 21:12.410
get rid of this haircut

21:12.410 --> 21:13.820
and my beard.

21:14.100 --> 21:15.630
Come on, I'll take you home.

21:17.200 --> 21:18.200
Home?

21:24.440 --> 21:27.510
[Speeding Auto House]

21:55.560 --> 21:56.890
What's gotten into you?

21:59.690 --> 22:01.260
Jiang Mu told me

22:01.890 --> 22:04.370
I'd look fresher this way.

22:16.340 --> 22:17.500
So, what do you think?

22:17.500 --> 22:19.360
Still as handsome as ever, right?

22:20.340 --> 22:21.260
But I think

22:21.580 --> 22:23.580
I'm a bit more handsome than you now.

22:25.860 --> 22:26.430
Here.

22:36.370 --> 22:37.300
I'm back.

22:38.210 --> 22:39.470
-Mu, you're here.
-Mu.

22:51.930 --> 22:53.020
Sanlai?

22:57.060 --> 22:58.170
You... you...

22:58.740 --> 23:00.340
Why do you look like this now?

23:03.820 --> 23:04.650
Like what?

23:05.740 --> 23:07.610
You had a haircut and you shaved?

23:10.100 --> 23:12.430
I didn't know your features were so sharp.

23:12.930 --> 23:15.390
It's the first time
I've seen your forehead.

23:16.560 --> 23:18.630
This style is so trendy,

23:18.650 --> 23:20.580
like an idol.

23:21.500 --> 23:23.900
How do you like it?
I just bought all of this.

23:24.240 --> 23:26.130
You look much cooler this way.

23:26.690 --> 23:27.930
These beads are so cute.

23:27.930 --> 23:28.780
Do they come in colors?

23:28.780 --> 23:29.970
I want the same ones.

23:30.130 --> 23:31.740
I got them for 19.90
at the store next door.

23:31.740 --> 23:32.360
What about this?

23:32.360 --> 23:33.050
Look.

23:36.780 --> 23:37.970
Not bad, really.

23:40.450 --> 23:41.130
Jiang Mu.

23:41.330 --> 23:42.860
Look at this. Do you like it?

23:44.780 --> 23:45.580
Jiang Mu!

23:47.650 --> 23:48.340
Come here.

23:49.890 --> 23:50.690
I'll go first.

24:06.450 --> 24:08.260
Did you see Sanlai?

24:08.410 --> 24:10.450
He's completely changed.

24:10.480 --> 24:13.540
-Completely...
-I hear you always ask Sanlai about me.

24:13.860 --> 24:15.060
What did you find out?

24:16.210 --> 24:17.610
Not much.

24:17.930 --> 24:19.240
You know him. He always

24:19.260 --> 24:20.740
goes off on tangents

24:20.860 --> 24:22.690
and can't stop praising himself.

24:22.690 --> 24:24.300
But I have to say, with this new look,

24:24.300 --> 24:25.780
he's actually quite handsome.

24:25.780 --> 24:26.890
Look at how he's...

24:34.540 --> 24:35.820
You're not mad

24:35.970 --> 24:37.610
because I always pry into your business,

24:37.610 --> 24:38.690
are you?

24:49.410 --> 24:51.670
Why do you want to know about my business?

24:51.740 --> 24:52.930
Because it's you.

25:15.280 --> 25:16.480
You know very well

25:22.130 --> 25:23.860
that we're not blood‑related.

25:24.930 --> 25:27.590
We lived together for a while
when we were young,

25:28.820 --> 25:30.750
but back then you were just a child.

25:37.970 --> 25:39.100
Now,

25:44.500 --> 25:45.700
you keep coming here.

25:47.930 --> 25:50.130
What will others think if they find out?

25:50.650 --> 25:52.110
What will Jin Qiang think?

26:03.020 --> 26:04.260
Or do you just...

26:07.470 --> 26:09.070
want something to happen...

26:16.710 --> 26:17.990
between us?

26:43.570 --> 26:44.220
Mu!

26:44.540 --> 26:45.610
I'll bring... I...

26:51.690 --> 26:52.890
What's going on here?

26:53.920 --> 26:56.920
[Jin's Chinese Restaurant]

26:55.340 --> 26:57.070
Three cases of beer.

26:58.980 --> 27:00.370
Three cases of beer. That's correct.

27:00.370 --> 27:02.000
Why doesn't it add up?

27:13.100 --> 27:13.890
Hello.

27:14.930 --> 27:15.840
It's you again.

27:15.860 --> 27:17.740
We have customers.
Go sleep somewhere else.

27:17.740 --> 27:19.670
Go sleep somewhere else! Hurry up!

27:20.860 --> 27:22.540
Hello.

27:23.370 --> 27:24.410
I'm sorry.

27:25.740 --> 27:27.260
We've sold out of all our dishes today.

27:27.260 --> 27:28.650
Only dumplings are left.

27:28.650 --> 27:30.650
Meat or vegetable dumplings?

27:30.780 --> 27:31.860
Which one would you like?

27:31.860 --> 27:32.920
You recommend one.

27:34.500 --> 27:36.160
Okay then. Please take a seat.

27:46.690 --> 27:47.420
You're here.

27:55.210 --> 27:56.300
Here are your dumplings.

27:56.300 --> 27:57.020
Thank you.

27:57.450 --> 27:58.850
The condiments are here.

27:59.610 --> 28:00.260
Alright?

28:01.580 --> 28:02.100
Zhao.

28:02.540 --> 28:04.140
Zhao, help me watch the shop.

28:04.280 --> 28:05.260
There's a customer inside.

28:05.260 --> 28:06.650
Give him whatever he asks for.

28:06.650 --> 28:08.910
-Okay.
-I'll go get something next door.

28:42.170 --> 28:43.890
Yours looks more delicious.

28:49.390 --> 28:51.220
My dumplings are too salty.

28:51.860 --> 28:53.710
Your fried rice looks...

28:54.060 --> 28:54.860
pretty good.

29:14.740 --> 29:16.060
Finish your food and leave.

29:16.060 --> 29:17.320
Don't come back again.

29:19.860 --> 29:21.520
I'm here to return something.

29:21.960 --> 29:22.960
Let's have a talk.

29:28.020 --> 29:30.220
Was that you on the mountain that night?

29:35.770 --> 29:37.650
I never expected the person
I've been looking for all this time

29:37.650 --> 29:38.540
to be you.

29:39.540 --> 29:40.670
Don't you remember?

29:40.820 --> 29:42.970
Last time you barged into my racing team

29:42.970 --> 29:44.770
when I wasn't paying attention.

29:45.410 --> 29:46.780
And the boxing match.

30:37.170 --> 30:38.970
I want you to fight a match for me.

30:40.100 --> 30:43.030
Your opponent
is He Zhang from Wan Shengbang's team.

30:46.690 --> 30:47.500
If you win,

30:47.930 --> 30:49.460
I'll give you a sum of money.

30:51.690 --> 30:54.020
I'll let you know
the time and place later.

30:55.260 --> 30:56.320
I didn't expect you

30:56.930 --> 30:59.060
to run away halfway through the fight.

31:00.430 --> 31:02.230
Then a pink pickup showed up,

31:02.930 --> 31:04.730
and the owner actually admitted

31:04.740 --> 31:06.740
that he was the one driving that night.

31:06.740 --> 31:09.270
I agreed to race him,
though I was suspicious.

31:10.130 --> 31:10.930
That guy

31:11.370 --> 31:12.900
was arranged by you, right?

31:17.690 --> 31:18.610
One race,

31:19.580 --> 31:20.580
just the two of us.

31:22.780 --> 31:23.710
There's no need.

31:27.580 --> 31:29.340
Liang Yanfeng drives faster than me.

31:29.340 --> 31:31.200
Why don't you go find him instead?

31:32.940 --> 31:34.600
I've known him for many years.

31:35.540 --> 31:36.980
He's never beaten me.

31:38.890 --> 31:39.820
But you have.

31:43.980 --> 31:45.820
That's because I know the roads better.

31:45.820 --> 31:47.280
Just happened to be lucky.

31:47.340 --> 31:48.410
One more time.

31:49.890 --> 31:50.820
Not interested.

31:50.820 --> 31:51.820
So what

31:52.780 --> 31:54.310
would make you interested?

31:59.020 --> 32:00.060
Eat up.

32:25.410 --> 32:26.450
I got information

32:26.860 --> 32:28.970
that next up is the cornering speed race.

32:28.970 --> 32:29.930
Get prepared.

32:30.930 --> 32:32.290
Only one race left,

32:33.970 --> 32:35.370
and you can make the top 3.

32:36.690 --> 32:37.750
I'm not confident.

32:39.210 --> 32:40.210
Last time,

32:41.970 --> 32:43.020
I almost lost.

32:44.540 --> 32:45.940
There's still some time.

32:46.260 --> 32:47.460
Only by getting first

32:47.690 --> 32:49.420
can you transport their cargo.

32:49.870 --> 32:52.300
That way, Wan Shengbang's
secret business will be cut off,

32:52.300 --> 32:53.830
and we'll get the evidence.

33:05.470 --> 33:07.380
What's wrong? Having problems?

33:19.060 --> 33:20.060
How did you

33:21.690 --> 33:22.650
drive back then?

33:37.340 --> 33:39.210
As a top racer,

33:41.100 --> 33:42.370
one obviously needs

33:43.450 --> 33:44.410
calmness,

33:45.410 --> 33:46.410
attentiveness,

33:47.860 --> 33:49.100
courage,

33:50.210 --> 33:50.970
and skill.

33:53.370 --> 33:55.170
All of this...

33:57.260 --> 33:58.590
is bullshit.

34:04.740 --> 34:06.800
So what's really the most important?

34:18.280 --> 34:19.110
Mastery.

34:20.110 --> 34:22.510
You need to master everything

34:22.530 --> 34:24.370
you're supposed to control.

34:24.889 --> 34:25.739
What is a car?

34:26.489 --> 34:28.530
A car is an extension of your body.

34:28.780 --> 34:29.699
And you

34:30.340 --> 34:32.489
should become part of the car,

34:33.610 --> 34:35.010
the most essential part.

34:35.449 --> 34:38.300
You need to understand its breathing,

34:39.050 --> 34:40.340
its rhythm,

34:40.570 --> 34:42.050
its sound,

34:44.449 --> 34:45.659
and its temperature.

34:53.889 --> 34:54.659
Of course,

34:55.050 --> 34:56.380
with just these things,

34:56.780 --> 34:57.890
it's not enough

34:58.220 --> 34:59.820
for one to become a top racer.

35:00.930 --> 35:02.260
You need to be so skilled

35:02.700 --> 35:04.490
that your hands
are faster than your brain,

35:04.490 --> 35:06.180
making all your movements

35:06.460 --> 35:08.150
become muscle memory

35:09.180 --> 35:10.840
and every decision and action

35:11.340 --> 35:12.740
happens instinctively,

35:14.570 --> 35:15.820
without thinking.

35:16.330 --> 35:18.140
Want to know how to achieve this?

35:18.570 --> 35:20.570
Come help me deliver food tomorrow.

35:23.290 --> 35:24.650
Let your body

35:25.410 --> 35:27.110
drive your car.

35:36.590 --> 35:37.620
Is there a simpler way to put it?

35:37.620 --> 35:38.220
Yes.

35:39.370 --> 35:40.370
Don't be a coward.

35:41.260 --> 35:41.990
I'm leaving.

35:45.890 --> 35:46.850
Drive carefully.

35:46.850 --> 35:47.910
Drink moderately.

35:48.710 --> 35:49.820
I'll come see you tomorrow.

35:49.820 --> 35:50.700
You brat.

36:09.010 --> 36:10.140
Or do you just...

36:11.820 --> 36:13.420
want something to happen...

36:14.760 --> 36:15.950
between us?

36:16.410 --> 36:17.450
So annoying.

36:19.150 --> 36:25.240
[Speeding Auto House]

36:22.610 --> 36:23.700
Jiang Mu,

36:23.890 --> 36:25.490
I made seafood hotpot today.

36:25.740 --> 36:27.600
Come over tonight and eat with us.

36:31.810 --> 36:33.210
She replied pretty fast.

36:34.410 --> 36:35.500
I'm eating vegetarian tonight.

36:35.500 --> 36:36.500
I won't be coming.

36:43.590 --> 36:44.700
Did you say something

36:44.700 --> 36:45.610
to Jiang Mu?

36:45.780 --> 36:47.780
She hasn't been coming over lately.

36:53.050 --> 36:53.820
I did.

37:09.140 --> 37:10.320
Can you cook faster?

37:10.490 --> 37:12.050
Can you drive faster?

37:12.860 --> 37:13.860
I'd like to drive faster.

37:13.860 --> 37:15.620
The rotors on your car
are completely worn out.

37:15.620 --> 37:17.010
If I drive any faster, it will fall apart.

37:17.010 --> 37:18.180
Just step on it.

37:18.580 --> 37:20.740
If you can wreck it, I'll be impressed.

37:23.020 --> 37:24.410
Turn off the AC while driving.

37:24.410 --> 37:25.620
The food
will taste different if it gets cold.

37:25.620 --> 37:27.480
People will say my cooking is bad.

37:28.490 --> 37:29.180
Got it.

37:29.890 --> 37:30.950
Come back quickly.

37:31.340 --> 37:33.670
We still have 7 or 8 more orders
to deliver.

38:03.790 --> 38:05.990
When will my food arrive? I'm starving.

38:07.370 --> 38:08.140
Ten minutes.

38:08.890 --> 38:10.220
Why is it taking so long?

38:10.220 --> 38:12.080
Your restaurant's delivery is too slow.

38:12.080 --> 38:13.740
I'm going to file a complaint.

39:04.050 --> 39:05.080
If you had come before 7,

39:05.080 --> 39:07.210
she wouldn't have thrown water on you.

39:49.320 --> 39:52.470
♪ See the light that pulls me far ♪

39:54.670 --> 39:57.820
♪ Chase the whispers where you are ♪

40:00.540 --> 40:03.760
♪ Through the echoing that still string ♪

40:05.980 --> 40:09.130
♪ Every step that takes me away ♪

40:07.860 --> 40:09.060
So it was just a dream.

40:10.350 --> 40:15.970
♪ Away from the noise and endless fights ♪

40:12.410 --> 40:13.820
This is too much.

40:14.180 --> 40:15.710
Can't you control yourself

40:15.780 --> 40:17.450
and stop thinking about all this nonsense?

40:16.470 --> 40:21.720
♪  Through the quite of your light ♪

40:18.780 --> 40:19.970
But what does he

40:20.410 --> 40:21.890
really think of me?

40:22.040 --> 40:27.220
♪ I'll break the chains of life's gray ♪

40:27.790 --> 40:33.720
♪ Take me far and take me away ♪

40:28.620 --> 40:31.090
Am I overthinking this?

40:33.050 --> 40:34.180
Or do you just...

40:36.700 --> 40:37.820
want something to happen...

40:36.740 --> 40:39.710
♪ Wind is howling and calling me ♪

40:41.500 --> 40:45.470
♪ Through the forest to the sea ♪

40:45.930 --> 40:47.180
between us?

40:47.690 --> 40:51.720
♪ Shadows dances, the sky turns grey ♪

40:52.750 --> 40:56.720
♪ But your voice still leads my ♪

40:58.360 --> 41:03.720
♪ Away from the noise and endless fights ♪

41:04.710 --> 41:09.710
♪  Through the quite of your light ♪

41:10.020 --> 41:14.720
♪ I'll break the chains of life's gray ♪

41:13.050 --> 41:14.570
So annoying.

41:15.400 --> 41:21.230
♪ Take me far and take me away ♪

41:15.530 --> 41:16.700
Could it be...

41:17.220 --> 41:18.570
that he was serious...

41:19.660 --> 41:20.930
about what he said?

41:23.050 --> 41:26.730
♪ The stars are whispering secrets true ♪

41:28.370 --> 41:33.230
♪ A pass unknown yet I'll pursue ♪

41:33.880 --> 41:38.130
♪ With every breath I hear you say ♪

41:38.480 --> 41:42.730
♪ You're waiting for me come away ♪

41:41.660 --> 41:42.890
It's already dawn.

41:43.640 --> 41:48.730
♪ Away from the noise and endless fights ♪

41:45.660 --> 41:46.860
Jiang Mu,

41:47.660 --> 41:49.370
pull yourself together.

41:49.820 --> 41:52.220
Otherwise,
how are you going to face him in the future?

41:49.890 --> 41:54.980
♪  Through the quite of your light ♪
